channel.title: Minute edits to JLW
channel.description:
[img]http://img337.imageshack.us/img337/4827/jenniferlovehewittjo1.jpg[/img]
^ The original stock for JLW.
[img]http://img178.imageshack.us/img178/8256/evokkijlwcopylv2.png[/img]
^ My edits:
Changed eye colour Changed shade on her lips for a more lucious colour Rosed up her cheeks abit Tucked up her chin Narrowed her face Made the area around her eyes more darker Changed the width of the nose for a lower profile Added obvious photofilters - Warming and colding filters, mainly warming for the final effect
Can anyone give me some C&C, possibly a rating out of 10 also ?

item.title: Minute edits to JLW
item.dc:creator: @I_Br3ndan_I I Br3ndan I
item.description:
@I_Br3ndan_I wrote:

Ugh, it does look good, but to be honest, I prefer the original. Girls with alot of make-up on just don’t appeal to me at all, it actually pisses me off. That’s what the second one looks like;she’s slapped alot of make-up on.

Saying that, you’ve done a great job of doing that, so I’d give it an 8/10. I can’t really comment on you’re methods and such 'cause I don’t know much in that sense, sorry.
